t our production facilities to enable real-time monitoring of our operations, system modifications, troubleshooting, increasing equipment life and automatic report generation. We believe that these systems assist us in reducing production times and expenses, while maintaining desired hygiene standards and operational efficiencies.

## Production Capacity and Capacity Utilization

